{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-14","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 14","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Hajde da malo pričamo o oblasti/polju u tehnologiji.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">UX (User Experience)</span> odnosi se na jednostavnost i uživanje u korišćenju nečega poput veb stranice ili aplikacije. Fokusira se na osiguravanje da sve radi dobro i da je prijatno za upotrebu.\r\n<span class=\"highlighted-text\">UI (User Interface)</span> tiče se načina na koji izgledaju stvari na veb stranici ili aplikaciji i gde ih možete pronaći. Uključuje dugmad koja kliknete, boje i raspored. Radi se o osiguravanju da sve izgleda dobro i da je lako dostupno.</p>\n<p>Pošto ste <span class=\"highlighted-text\">UX designer</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">UI designer</span>, ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">UX/UI designer</span>, vi ste osoba odgovorna za to da sajtovi i programi budu laki za korišćenje i da izgledaju dobro.</p>\n<p>Dopuni rečenice popunjavanjem praznih delova.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"","explanation":null,"challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","block":"learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-14"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Alice: What does she do on the team?</p>\n<p>Tom: She's a BLANK/BLANK designer. She's really creative.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"UX","feedback":"<p>Kratki opis za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">User Experience</span>, tiče se osiguravanja da sve radi i da je lako za korišćenje.</p>"},{"answer":"UI","feedback":"<p>Fupi ya <span class=\"highlighted-text\">User Interface</span>, odnosi se na izgled i osećaj sajta ili aplikacije.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Alice","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0},{"character":"Tom","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"4.3-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":16.42,"finishTimestamp":20.96},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Alice","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Alice","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.06,"dialogue":{"text":"What does she do on the team?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Alice","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.26,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":2.26,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.46,"finishTime":5.54,"dialogue":{"text":"She's a UX/UI designer. She's really creative.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Tom","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":6.04,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","dashedName":"task-14","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interactions/task-15","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-clarify-information-in-different-interact